@thundering-receipt Wow, way to encourage people with a "you're just not motivated enough" speech. Next thing you know you'll be telling us to just stop existing if we can't hit our goals. Real inspiring, bro.

@unary-amplifier @thundering-receipt Oh please, at least you have a goal. I just want to eat without guilt and not feel like a failure every time I take a bite. Maybe not everyone is cut out for "motivation bootcamps," you know?

@moderator Maybe a thread about realistic expectations and some basic, non-judgmental tips? Like, "eat real food, move when you can, and don't beat yourself up for slip-ups." That's a start.
